arts.ttl: Frustrated Portsmouth boss rues creativity problems after first Fratton Park defeat in 3 months as Millwall triumph
arts.sum: John Mousinho rued Pompey’s lack of quality in the final third as they slumped to a first Fratton Park defeat in three months.

arts.ttl: Portsmouth £1.27m new boy answers big question on his Championship adjustment after whirlwind debut
arts.sum: Hayden Matthews is confident he will adjust to the pace and power of the Championship after his Pompey debut.

arts.ttl: Portsmouth boss addresses Ryley Towler's surprise absence amid intense transfer window interest
arts.sum: John Mousinho insists Ryley Towler’s surprise absence from Pompey’s 1-0 defeat to Millwall was down to selection.

arts.ttl: Millwall boss Neil has praise for matchwinner Ivanovic and Bangura-Williams after 1-0 win at Portsmouth
arts.sum: Young midfielder Ra’ees Bangura-Williams atoned for missing an early sitter by playing the pass through for Ivanovic to lift the ball beyond Pompey keeper Nicolas Schmid in the first half. Neil said: “Luton was probably a bit more controlled than tonight was.

arts.ttl: ‘Key lapse’, ‘unusually sloppy’, ‘attacks of grace’: Jordan Cross’ Portsmouth ratings from Millwall defeat
arts.sum: The ratings are in from Pompey’s frustrating defeat to Millwall.

arts.ttl: Portsmouth 0 Millwall 1: Neil Allen's verdict - Wasteful Blues have themselves to blame in infuriating defeat
arts.sum: The rest may well have done them some good, yet, ultimately, it was a lack of quality which proved Pompey’s downfall.

arts.ttl: Millwall battle to narrow win at Portsmouth
arts.sum: Mihailo Ivanovic and Ra'ees Bangura-Williams gave Millwall fans a sense of deja vu as they combined for the only goal in a 1-0 victory for the second match in a row.

arts.ttl: Portsmouth beaten as Millwall duo combine again
arts.sum: Ra’ees Bangura-Williams set up Mihailo Ivanovic’s winner for the second match in a row.

arts.ttl: Portsmouth boss restores big players and hands surprise debut - but still notable absences against Millwall
arts.sum: John Mousinho has reverted to his strongest available Pompey side for tonight’s Millwall clash - but there are still some noticeable absences.

arts.ttl: New Portsmouth signing reveals reasons behind £1.2m transfer as he prepares for potential debut v Millwall
arts.sum: Hayden Matthews has confessed a move to Pompey was too good an opportunity to turn down.
